"sp-site" is example of web site that demonstrate using of futures.
Beside this, example preparing you to use a new pattern/paradigm Data Middleware View(DMV) as better alternative comparing to MVC.

Before run example you should compile "prepare_app_.js" module using the following command: $ node-streamline -c prepare_app_.js 
This will create a file "prepare_app.js" that can be used as regular kind of javascript module.

For details regarding benefits of using "streamline" library go to the following link:
http://github.com/Sage/streamlinejs




